      "message": "Since this function will typically be generating files, I feel like maybe this should be a WriteCloser so that Downloader can manage closing the files as opposed to the user. This is especially painful for the user since this function gets called in a thread-unsafe way, so if it modifies any closed-over variables, they will need locks. :/",
