      "writtenOn": "2017-12-04T15:26:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You feel you need this because the caller lacks context to be able to know when it\u0027s done. By this, the client is effectively passing ownership to the Download.\n\nWhy do you feel that the client cannot manage the lifetime of the handle? What\u0027s the gain, vs fully blocking Fetch calls?",
      "parentUuid": "15365058_d7c48b3c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 32,
